<view class="page"><scroll-view class="scroll" scroll-y enhanced show-scrollbar="{{false}}"><view class="title has-back"><text class="back" bindtap="goBack">‹</text>课后评价清单</view><view class="subtitle">U10提高班 · <text>本节课已完成</text></view><view class="progress-card"><view class="progress-icon">▣</view><view><text>已完成 <text class="strong">{{completedCount}}</text>/{{totalCount}}</text><view class="track"><view style="width:{{progressWidth}}%"></view></view></view></view><view class="student" wx:for="{{students}}" wx:key="id" data-id="{{item.id}}" data-index="{{item.index}}" bindtap="openEvaluation"><image src="{{item.avatar}}" mode="aspectFill"/><text class="name">{{item.name}}</text><text class="status {{item.statusClass}}">{{item.status}}</text><text class="action">{{item.actionLabel}}　›</text></view><view class="package">▣　<view><text>完成评价后生成成长包</text><text class="small">包含本节课堂评价与教练反馈，助力孩子成长</text></view></view><view class="safe"></view></scroll-view><view class="footer" bindtap="finishAll">{{finishLabel}}　›</view></view>
